Windows Only
Install MySQL Installer 8.0.15 and Select all the packets below
https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/windows/installer/8.0.html

Install MySQL Workbench 8.0.15 
https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/workbench/

Install MySQL Connector/J 5.1.47 or 8.0.15 
https://dev.mysql.com/doc/relnotes/connector-j/5.1/en/news-5-1-47.html 	
https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/connector/j/8.0.html - Must use the installer above for windows

Install MySQL Server 8.0.15
https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/mysql/

Windows Only
Install MySQL Installer 8.0.15 and Select all the packets below
https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/windows/installer/8.0.html

In netbeans you need to add the downloaded connector to your projects Libraries by Right clickinging and selecting Add JAR/folder, navigate to the connector folder and select the .jar
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nW13FmTdkjc